<concept xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="bookmap" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:concept.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Bookmap</title>
  <conbody>
    <p id="bookmap-definition">A <term>bookmap</term><indexterm>DITA bookmap</indexterm> is a <xref href="dita-specialization-serna-free.xml">specialization</xref> of  <xref href="map-serna-free.xml">DITA map</xref> that allows you to organize your <xref href="dita-topics-serna-free.xml">DITA topics</xref> into a collection that can be printed as a book or other paged layout.
</p>
    <fig>
      <title>DITA Bookmap opened in Serna.</title>
      <image href="dita-bookmap-opened-in-serna.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
    </fig>
    <p>You can find more information about bookmaps at: <xref href="http://docs.oasis-open.org/dita/v1.1/OS/archspec/HowToUse.html" format="html"/></p>
  </conbody>
  <related-links>
    <link href="dita-maps-xslt-parameter-sets-serna-free.xml"/>
  </related-links>
</concept>
